<div id="acknowledgments">

<h3>Acknowledgments</h3>

<p>
We thank Robyn Bluhm and Maya Goldenberg for their comments on the
original version of the entry, and Thomas Bonnin for his helpful
comments on this version. We also thank the organizers and
participants of &ldquo;Trajectories of Epistemic Injustice in
Philosophy of Medicine &ndash; A Workshop with Miranda Fricker&rdquo;
(Bielefeld University), especially Lara Keuck, for helpful discussions
on the scope of epistemic injustice and its limitations.</p>
